"tú RKWard.</p>"

#: rkward/misc/rkdynamicsearchline.cpp:24
#, kde-format
msgid "Search"
msgstr "Cuardaigh"

#: rkward/misc/rkdynamicsearchline.cpp:46
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p><b>Note:</b> This search line accepts so-called regular expressions. To "
"limit the search to matches at the start of the string, start the filter "
"with '^', e.g. ('^rk.'). To limit searches to the end of the string, append "
"'$' at the end of the filter. To match arbitrary text in the middle of the "
"search term, insert '.*'.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><b>Nóta:</b> Glacann an líne chuardaigh seo le habairtí rialta mar a "
"thugtar orthu. Chun an cuardach a theorannú do mheaitseálacha ag tús an "
"teaghráin, tosaigh an scagaire le '^', m.sh. ('^rk.'). Chun cuardaigh a "
"theorannú do dheireadh an teaghráin, cuir '$' ag deireadh an scagaire. Chun "
"téacs treallach a mheaitseáil i lár an téarma cuardaigh, cuir isteach '.*'.</"
"p>"

#: rkward/misc/rkfindbar.cpp:54
#, kde-format
msgid "Search backwards (previous occurrence of search term)"
